    "rationale": "The credibility assessment is accepted for regulatory submission under the Minimal profile. All 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors have been addressed; seven factors were formally assessed (all achieving level 3 against required level 4) and six factors were flagged as not-assessed epistemic gaps at MRL 5. The submission is accepted with the explicit understanding that the six not-assessed factors constitute open action items to be resolved prior to final regulatory clearance. A sha256 content hash (sha256:a3f8c2e14b76d905f1e2a9c3d84b7f620e5c1a9d3b8e4f7c2a6d0e9b5f3c8a1d) is recorded for traceability. The digital signature has not yet been applied — the ed25519 signature workflow is pending scheduling with the independent review board and will be appended as an amendment. Structural integrity of this package cannot be cryptographically verified until the signature is affixed.",
